org.afplib.afplib

Interface ICP

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ICPImpl

    public interface ICP
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'ICP'.

    The following features are supported:

    • XC Oset
    • YC Oset
    • XC Size
    • YC Size
    • XFil Size
    • YFil Size

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getICP()
